comment: * This class represents meta-data that describes a PDF {@link Page}.

methods.name: public int getPageWidth()
methods.comment:
* Gets the page width in PostScript points (1/72th of an inch).
         *
         * @return The page width.

methods.name: public int getPageHeight()
methods.comment:
* Gets the page height in PostScript points (1/72th of an inch).
         *
         * @return The page height.

methods.name: public Rect getContentRect()
methods.comment:
* Get the content rectangle in PostScript points (1/72th of an inch).
         * This is the area that contains the page content and is relative to
         * the page top left.
         *
         * @return The content rectangle.

methods.name: public int getPageNumber()
methods.comment:
* Gets the page number.
         *
         * @return The page number.
